author: RTÉ News
title: Panama allows virus-affected ship to pass through canal
description: Panama's government gave permission to a cruise ship on which four passengers have died to travel through its canal, a day after blocking the liner over coronavirus fears.
content:
Panama's government gave permission to a cruise ship on which four passengers have died to travel through its canal, a day after blocking the liner over coronavirus fears.
